Ihe ndị a bụ ndepụta usoro ahịrị ụzọ ụgbọ oloko si aga na  okporo ígwè na China
Maka ụgbọ oloko nke nwere ike iga ọsọ ọsọ, lee Ndepụta nke ahịrị ụgbọ okporo ígwè dị elu na China

N'ime ihe gbasara ọrụ ụgbọ oloko, a na akpọ kọta Jingshan Railway, Shenshan Railway, Changda Railway | Changda Railway, Changchun - Shenyang Portion na Changbin Railway otu aha nke bụ Jingha Railway ( Beijing - Harbin).
Jingjiu Railway na -eji otu ahịrị dị ka Guangmeishan Railway n'etiti Longchuan na Dongguan
Ọ na -ejikwa otu ahịrị dịka Guangshen Railway n'etiti Dongguan na Shenzhen
Ọ gafere ókè ahụ wee soro ụzọ ụgbọ oloko East ruo Kowloon, Hong Kong.
